08(1 + O(v2)); (5:3)

The parameter H08 estimated in [2,17] lies between 1.4 and 3.0 MeV. We take H08 = 2:0MeV. The numerical result for the total cross section in nb as a function of psflp = p(q + p)2 in GeV is given in Fig.5. At PT = 3GeV the dominant contribution comes from photon-gluon fusion, while the processes with quark or antiquark as the initial partons contribute only with the fraction at order of 10\Gamma 3.

